    "body": "Perhaps a fancy thing we could do is wrap metrics calls in anonymous functions?\r\n```ts\r\nthis.metrics.maybe(() => this.metrics.someMetric.set(this.expensiveFunction());\r\n```\r\nMore a matter of taste whether that or a simple `if` suffices.\r\n```ts\r\nif (metrics) this.metrics.someMetric.set(this.expensiveFunction());\r\n```",
